{"type":"message","id":"efc80fc8","parentId":"1bb0095d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T02:57:21.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"JS 返回了 ok:false，说明没找到 contenteditable 元素，需要先重新 snapshot 看看当前页面结构，确认评论框的状态和正确的元素选择器。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没找到元素。让我先重新 snapshot 看看当前页面结构：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0ca0d79de7294213b48385ce","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"snapshot","targetId":"FC930C029CE4B103E42586BAF9DE84E0","refs":"aria"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":224528,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":224692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772506621134}}
